WEBVTT

00:00:00.708 --> 00:00:02.476
Adam Grant: Hey everyone. It's Adam.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:04.809
If this is your first time
listening to WorkLife,

00:00:04.833 --> 00:00:06.101
don't start here.

00:00:06.125 --> 00:00:07.518
This is a bonus episode.

00:00:07.542 --> 00:00:11.226
To get the full WorkLife experience,
start with "How to Love Criticism,"

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:14.643
"Your Hidden Personality,"
"The Creative Power of Misfits,"

00:00:14.667 --> 00:00:17.726
or "The Real Reason You Procrastinate."

00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:19.208
Don't put that one off.

